public abstract class WPPredicateGenerator
extends BasePredicateGenerator

Generates predicates based on the weakest pre-condition of existing predicates This class solely handles the part that generates new predicate(s) Call the constructor Function to initiate. Call the function newPred() to return a list of Predicates
